{[%mdl 8256] C50: Hungarian Defence and Giuoco Pianissimo} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6
3. Bc4 Bc5 4. d3 a6 $146 {Controls b5} (4... Nge7 5. Ng5 d5 6. exd5 Nxd5 7. Nc3
Be6 8. Nxe6 fxe6 9. Ne4 Bb6 10. Qh5+ g6 11. Qh6 Nce7 12. Qg7 Rf8 13. Qxe5 Qd7
14. Bh6 Nc6 15. Qg3 Rf5 16. Bg5 Nd4 17. Rc1 h6 18. Bxh6 O-O-O 19. c3 {Rabiega,
R (2485)-Loerke,R (2190) Dresden 2000 1-0}) (4... Nf6 5. Nc3 $11) 5. Nbd2 (5.
Ng5 $5 {should not be overlooked} Nh6 6. a4 $14) 5... Nf6 $11 6. O-O d5 (6...
O-O $5 $11 {must be considered}) 7. exd5 $14 Nxd5 {White has a cramped
position. White's piece can't move: c1} 8. Re1 f6 {Prevents intrusion on g5} 9.
a4 a5 (9... Be6 10. c3 O-O 11. d4 $14) 10. Nb3 (10. d4 Bxd4 11. Nb3 Nb6 $18)
10... Bb6 (10... Be7 $5 $16) 11. d4 O-O (11... Nde7 $142 12. c3 Qd6 $18) 12.
dxe5 $18 Be6 13. exf6 Re8 (13... Nf4 14. Bxe6+ Nxe6 15. Qxd8 Ncxd8 16. fxg7
Nxg7 $18) 14. Rxe6 $1 {Remove defender: e6} Rxe6 15. Qxd5 Qxd5 16. Bxd5 Rd8 (
16... Rae8 {does not solve anything} 17. Ng5 Nd8 18. f7+ Nxf7 19. Bxe6 $18) 17.
Bxe6+ Kf8 18. Bg5 gxf6 19. Bxf6 Rd6 20. Re1 h5 21. Ng5 Nd4 22. Nxd4 Bxd4 23.
Bxd4 (23. Nh7+ Ke8 24. Bf5+ Be5 25. Rxe5+ Kf7 26. Re7+ Kg8 27. Re8+ Kf7 28.
Rf8#) 23... Rxd4 $18 24. Bb3 c5 25. Ne6+ Kg8 26. Nxd4+ Kh7 27. Nf3 c4 28. Bxc4
b5 (28... Kg7 {cannot undo what has already been done} 29. Re7+ Kf8 30. Rxb7
Ke8 31. Ne5 Kd8 32. Nc6+ Ke8 33. Be6 Kf8 34. h4 Ke8 35. Rb8#) 29. axb5 a4 (
29... h4 {cannot change destiny} 30. b6 Kg6 31. b7 Kf5 32. b8=Q a4 33. Qg8 a3
34. Qg5#) 30. b6 a3 (30... Kg7 {does not save the day} 31. b7 a3 32. b8=Q h4
33. Qc7+ Kh6 34. Qf7 axb2 35. Re6#) 31. b7 a2 (31... Kg6 {does not improve
anything} 32. b8=Q h4 33. Qb6+ Kh5 34. Re5+ Kg4 35. Qd4#) 32. b8=Q h4 (32...
a1=R {is not the saving move} 33. Qg8+ Kh6 34. Qf8+ Kh7 35. Bd3#) 33. Qg8+ Kh6
34. Bd3 a1=Q 35. Qg6# (35. Qg5#) 1-0

