Kc4 64. Qf6 Kd5 65. Qd8+ Kc6 66. Kg4 Kb7 67. Kf5 Kc6 68. Ke4 Kc5 69. Qa5+ Kc4
70. Qd5+ Kc3 71. Qd3+ Kb2 72. Qb5+ Kc2 73. Qb4 Kd1 74. Qb2 Ke1 75. Ke3 Kd1 76.
Qd2#) 58. b5 Kc8 59. Kf6 Kc7 (59... Kd7 {doesn't get the cat off the tree} 60.
Ke5 Kd8 61. b6 Kd7 62. Kd5 Kc8 63. c6 Kd8 64. Kd6 Ke8 65. c7 Kf7 66. c8=Q Kf6
67. Qg4 Kf7 68. Qg5 Kf8 69. Ke6 Ke8 70. Qe7#) 60. Ke7 Kc8 (60... Kb8 {doesn't
change anything anymore} 61. Kd6 Kc8 62. b6 Kb7 63. c6+ Kxb6 64. c7 Kb5 65. Kd5
Ka5 66. Kc4 Ka6 67. c8=Q+ Kb6 68. Qd7 Ka6 69. Kc5 Ka5 70. Qb5#) 61. Kd6 Kb7 (
61... Kb8 {doesn't change the outcome of the game} 62. c6 Ka7 63. Kc5 Kb8 64.
b6 Kc8 65. Kd6 Kd8 66. b7 Ke8 67. b8=Q+ Kf7 68. c7 Kg6 69. Qb1+ Kg5 70. c8=Q
Kh4 71. Qg1 Kh5 72. Qh3#) 62. c6+ Kc8 (62... Kb6 {hardly improves anything} 63.
