Ka3 70. Qbb4#) 63. b6 Kb8 (63... Kd8 {does not solve anything} 64. b7 Ke8 65.
b8=Q+ Kf7 66. c7 Kg7 67. Qb1 Kh6 68. c8=Q Kg7 69. Qbf5 Kh6 70. Qcf8#) 64. b7 (
