{[%mdl 8256] B34: Sicilian: Accelerated Dragon with 5 Nc3: sidelines} 1. d4 Nf6
2. Nf3 g6 3. Nc3 c5 4. e4 cxd4 5. Nxd4 Nc6 6. Nf3 $146 (6. f4 Qb6 7. Nf3 d6 8.
Bc4 Bg7 9. Qd3 O-O 10. Bb3 Bg4 11. Be3 Qa5 12. O-O Bxf3 13. gxf3 Qh5 14. Kh1
Rad8 15. Rad1 Qh3 16. Qe2 Nh5 17. Rg1 Kh8 18. Qf2 Qc8 19. f5 e6 20. Bg5 Bf6 {
Ljubojevic,L (2510)-Bilek,I (2485) Teeside 1972 1-0 (33)}) (6. Bg5 Bg7 7. Nb3
O-O 8. Qd2 a5 9. a4 d6 10. Bb5 Be6 11. Rd1 Rc8 12. O-O Nb4 13. Nd4 Bd7 14. Rfe1
Ng4 15. Re2 h6 16. Bh4 g5 17. Bg3 Ne5 18. b3 Ng6 19. Bxd7 Qxd7 20. Ncb5 Rfd8 {
Bojkovic,S (2216)-Milenkovic,M (2329) Kraljevo 2014 1/2-1/2 (50)}) (6. Nb3 Bg7
7. g3 d6 8. Bg2 Bg4 9. f3 Be6 10. f4 a5 11. Be3 a4 12. Nd4 a3 13. Nxe6 fxe6 14.
O-O axb2 15. Rb1 Ra3 16. Bd2 Qb6+ 17. Kh1 h5 18. e5 Ng4 19. Qe2 d5 20. Nb5 Rxa2
{Nilsson,N (2245)-Auchenberg,P (2240) Copenhagen 1984 0-1 (55)}) (6. Be2 e5 7.
Nf3 d6 8. O-O Be7 9. Re1 O-O 10. h3 Be6 11. Bf1 Qa5 12. Bd2 Qd8 13. Bc1 Qa5 14.
Bd2 Qd8 15. Na4 d5 16. exd5 Nxd5 17. Nxe5 Nxe5 18. Rxe5 Bf6 19. Re1 Rc8 20. c4
Nb6 {Liang,J (2415)-Tischbierek,R (2435) Timisoara 1987 1/2-1/2}) (6. Nxc6 dxc6
7. Qxd8+ Kxd8 $14) 6... Qa5 7. Bd3 {Black is behind in developement. Black's
piece can't move: c8} Bg7 {White has a very active position} 8. O-O O-O 9. a3 {
Controls b4} (9. Bd2 $5 $11) 9... d5 10. exd5 Nxd5 11. Nxd5 Qxd5 12. Be2 Qa5
13. c3 {Prevents intrusion on b4+d4} Rd8 14. Qc2 Bf5 {Black threatens to win
material: Bf5xc2} 15. Qb3 {White threatens to win material: Qb3xb7} Qc7 16. Be3
e5 17. Rfd1 Be6 {Black threatens to win material: Be6xb3} 18. Qc2 (18. Qa4 $142
$5 $11 {is worthy of consideration}) 18... Nd4 $17 19. Bxd4 exd4 20. Ng5 (20.
c4 Bf5 21. Bd3 Bg4 $17) 20... Bf5 21. Qb3 (21. Bd3 $142 Bxd3 22. Rxd3 dxc3 23.
bxc3 Rxd3 24. Qxd3 $17) 21... h6 $4 {gives away a clear win} (21... Qe7 $142 {
Black clearly has the better chances} 22. h4 dxc3 23. Rxd8+ Rxd8 24. bxc3 h6 (
24... Qxe2 $6 25. Qxf7+ Kh8 26. Qb3 $17) 25. Nxf7 Be6 (25... Qxf7 $4 26. Bc4
Rf8 27. Re1 $18) 26. Nxh6+ Bxh6 $19) 22. Nxf7 $1 $18 {a fitting end to a
beautiful game} Kh7 (22... Qxf7 23. Bc4 {Combination}) 23. Nxd8 Rxd8 24. Bd3 $4
{White loses the upper hand} (24. cxd4 {might be the shorter path} Bc2 25. Rdc1
Qxh2+ (25... Bxb3 $4 {going for material but overlooking...} 26. Rxc7 b6 27.
Rac1 $18) 26. Kxh2 Bxb3 $18) 24... Bg4 $4 {leads to further unpleasantness} (
24... dxc3 $142 25. Bxf5 cxb2 26. Bxg6+ Kxg6 $16) 25. f3 $18 Bd7 26. Qf7 (26.
cxd4 {might be the shorter path} Bxd4+ 27. Kh1 Bc6 $18) 26... Qb6 27. Kh1 Be8
28. Qe7 dxc3 $2 (28... Ba4 29. Re1 dxc3 $18) 29. bxc3 Kh8 (29... Rb8 {doesn't
do any good} 30. Rab1 Qf6 31. Rxb7 Rxb7 32. Qxb7 $18 (32. Qxe8 $6 {is the
weaker alternative} Qf7 33. Qe1 Re7 $18)) 30. h3 (30. Be4 $142 {makes it even
easier for White} Rc8 $18) 30... Bf6 $4 {leading to a quick end} (30... Ba4 31.
Rdb1 Qf6 $18) 31. Qf8+ Kh7 32. Bc4 h5 (32... Ba4 {praying for a miracle} 33.
Qf7+ Bg7 $18) 33. Bg8+ Kh8 34. Bf7+ Kh7 35. Qg8+ Kh6 1-0

