Bd2 Qc7 18. Be4 (18. Qb3 h6 $11) 18... Bxe4 19. Rxe4 Bd6 20. Rae1 Nf6 21. R4e2
c5 22. Bg5 cxd4 23. Qxd4 Be7 24. Qh4 h6 {Black threatens to win material: h6xg5
} 25. Bc1 Rd5 26. Qc4 {White threatens to win material: Qc4xc7} (26. c4 Ra5 27.
a3 Bd6 $11) 26... Rc5 27. Qb3 Bd6 {Black threatens to win material: Bd6xe5} 28.
