Bxd6 Rxd6 31. Ne5 $11) 30. Bxd6 {White forks: f8+c7} Qxd6 31. Nf4 {White
threatens to win material: Nf4xh5} Rxh2 32. Rxe6 $4 {White lets it slip away} (
32. Qxb7 $142 {and White can hope to live} Qc5 33. Nd3 $11) 32... Qc5 $19 (
