{[%mdl 8192] B11: Caro-Kann: Two Knights Variation} 1. e4 c6 2. Nf3 d5 3. Nc3
Bg4 4. d4 e6 5. Be2 Nf6 (5... Nd7 6. O-O Bb4 7. Ng5 Bxe2 8. Qxe2 Ne7 9. Qd3 h6
10. Nf3 O-O 11. Bd2 Ng6 12. Rfe1 Rc8 13. a3 Ba5 14. Rad1 Re8 15. g3 Nf6 16. e5
